# petit-prince.annotations
## Set of annotations to characterise the Petit Prince audiobooks (in English and French) heard in the scanner by the CNeuroMod participants.

Stimuli from **Jixing Li, John Hale, and Christophe Pallier (2025).** *Le Petit Prince: A multilingual fMRI corpus using ecological stimuli.* OpenNeuro. [Dataset] doi: doi:10.18112/openneuro.ds003643.v2.0.7
